and knuckled down.\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 2137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1897, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999997126501925, \"rank\": 2.8449286767582165e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympics 2024 medal table\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1870}, {\"ngram\": \"latest count\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1887}, {\"ngram\": \"more golds\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1923}, {\"ngram\": \"Day 11 Olympics\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"Every Team GB medal winner\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1975}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"little things\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's obviously these two's first Olympics and both of them stepped up to the occasion and have a medal to show for it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2257, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these two's first Olympics\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2179}, {\"ngram\": \"the occasion\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain's medal tally is guaranteed to grow on Wednesday night, with the men's team pursuit outfit certain of silver at least after setting up a clash with new world record holders Australia in the final.\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2259, \"end\": 2266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.6765573198501839, \"rank\": 0.4780712899851113, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2440, \"end\": 2449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_l